  - <ID>k__BackingField: d4ce026e-1625-41ea-9e6c-7e4dc07edb22
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 52b55f11-856a-434f-94a1-02ea6f61c8e6
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 179.2, y: 64}
    <Text>k__BackingField: Another reason for the adoption of a more gentler kind
      of masculinity in China's contemporary masculinity is also due to men having
      to taken on the nurturer's role
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
