  - <ID>k__BackingField: 52b55f11-856a-434f-94a1-02ea6f61c8e6
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName2
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: Continue...
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 82315d37-f628-4d6f-8616-90d4f90ee766
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 957.6, y: 64}
    <Text>k__BackingField: Due to the rising cost of living, there is a greater need
      for dual income household. As a result, fathers are increasing adopt a less
      authoritarian role and be more gentler
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6800915032177342135, guid: 97dbcf3c2e2539d489c7150e0fe63bd8, type: 3}
