      <NodeID>k__BackingField: de7b3002-5558-482a-b306-0fbd192081ec
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 2551.2, y: 67.2}
    <Text>k__BackingField: In contemporary China, women are expecting men to be better
      communicators. Chinese women also perceive traits like sensitivity and emotionally
      vulnerability as authentic.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
